00:01:34.320 --> 00:01:35.120 align:middle line:10%
>> Hello.

00:01:35.120 --> 00:01:39.140 align:middle line:84%
My name is Ocean Robbins,
and I'm 25 years old.

00:01:39.140 --> 00:01:42.290 align:middle line:10%
