practice, and awareness

00:04:23.900 --> 00:04:27.620 align:middle line:10%
with our generation that seems
to have been skipped over

00:04:27.620 --> 00:04:29.210 align:middle line:10%
in some ways.

00:04:29.210 --> 00:04:31.910 align:middle line:10%
So I'm just really glad
to be here with everybody

00:04:31.910 --> 00:04:37.182 align:middle line:10%
and look forward to getting
to interact tonight.

